{
  "stem": "10119.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I decided, being that I was with a group from Kaschau, to go back to Kaschau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did allow us to travel on the trains without any money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were taking us wherever we had to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever country we were in, they let us go free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just got a group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to the train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us where we wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, once I came to Kaschau, there was also-- we got together in one big place, all of us, we-- we met.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From there, there was-- I don't know how you would call it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- I think the owner might have already worked with them because there were places which we were able to go in and to see what's what.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were able to get some food and sleep over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just like a transit place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From there, some of my friends did go to Sweden, six girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And being that I have found somebody who was going home-- so I decided that I'm not going to Sweden with you, which I wish I would have.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they went a complete-- they were there for six weeks with-- with psychologists, which helped them out a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home to look for my family, which, with the train, there was also-- we always got a free ticket.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes you have to travel on the roof or sit on the floor, but we were always able to travel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're going to change tapes, and you tell me about what happened when you got back home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
